{"tid":883043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳水扁批金庸大中華膠","createTime":"2018-10-30T13:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T19:39:05.000Z","uid":144372,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f86a464f2b6af0965300f24e51e05393e86dac","tid":883043,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/general/200104/200104250060545.html#.W9hiCpMzbIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fcts%2Fgeneral%2F200104%2F200104250060545.html%23.W9hiCpMzbIU&d=4yQ6pjSs0bH3JieQ0wn1pZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a4190767\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/general/200104/200104250060545.html#.W9hiCpMzbIU</a><br />\n<br />\n武俠大師金庸在台灣才幾天的時間，引起不少話題，除了與李安的武林高峰會，離台前與陳水扁總統也有過招的機會，阿扁總統當面批評了大師的統派作風，面對指責，金庸不動聲色的在送給阿扁三本著作的題字上，表達了自己堅定態度。<br />\n<br />\n　　陳水扁總統在接見金庸時，先是以自己女兒也是金庸迷，捧了大師，不過接著就開始出招了。<br />\n<br />\n　　雖然金庸之前也曾為這個話題發火，不過，這回批他的好歹是位總統，大師為了顧全場面、忍住火氣，接著阿扁送了尊戰鬥力十足的關公像給大師，金庸則見招拆招，三本贈書裡，提的全是和平統一的立場。"},{"pid":"e9f6a2f7c30793505d523b51f643d19d071a3e45","tid":883043,"uid":127988,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:02:25.000Z","msg":"和平統一的立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搵李登輝即收呢條大中華膠皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfb710cccfcf6e98b40821e7c30fbdca91b9b73","tid":883043,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"阿扁真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6810f18ee0be6ddeb8d0678e35f16ece4e226682","tid":883043,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"真人大仆街"},{"pid":"2734ae05a2d4b7ebe68052b43118051871e2591f","tid":883043,"uid":109462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9f6a2f7c30793505d523b51f643d19d071a3e45","tid":883043,"uid":127988,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:02:25.000Z","msg":"和平統一的立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搵李登輝即收呢條大中華膠皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:11:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sRIW0IkuWEY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsRIW0IkuWEY&d=4yQ6pjSs0bH3JieQ0wn1pZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=692cbd25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sRIW0IkuWEY</a><br />\n<br />\n二十世紀的中國，是一個苦難的國家。先是外患不斷，而後，五十年來，又因意識形態的不同，造成「中國人打中國人」的悲劇，積累了同胞手足間的對立與仇恨。登輝一向主張，在邁進二十一世紀的前夕，海峽雙方都應致力結束歷史的悲劇，開創「中國人幫中國人」的新局。<br />\n<br />\n海峽兩岸沒有民族與文化認同問題，有的只是制度與生活方式之爭。在這裡，我們根本沒有必要，也不可能採行所謂「台獨」的路線。四十多年來，海峽兩岸因為歷史因素，而隔海分治，乃是事實；但是海峽雙方都以追求國家統一為目標，也是事實。<br />\n<br />\n海峽兩岸，都應該正視處理結束敵對狀態這項重大問題，以便為追求國家統一的歷史大業，作出關鍵性的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n登輝深信，在二十一世紀，中國人必能完成和平統一的歷史大業，為世界和平與發展，善盡更大的心力！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9045426e0a75d6e76b14d30b42f978164e293547","tid":883043,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2734ae05a2d4b7ebe68052b43118051871e2591f","tid":883043,"uid":109462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9f6a2f7c30793505d523b51f643d19d071a3e45","tid":883043,"uid":127988,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:02:25.000Z","msg":"和平統一的立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搵李登輝即收呢條大中華膠皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:11:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sRIW0IkuWEY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsRIW0IkuWEY&d=4yQ6pjSs0bH3JieQ0wn1pZWUQYxl